                  <h3
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 md:mb-2"
                  >
                    Sales Management
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm mb-2 md:mb-3">
                    Track and manage your entire sales process. Gain real-time
                    insights into sales performance and customer behavior.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-red-50 to-orange-50 p-4 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
