              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-red-50 to-orange-50 p-4 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h3
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 md:mb-2"
                  >
                    FBR Digital Invoicing
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm mb-2 md:mb-3">
                    Every invoice is submitted to FBR's Digital Invoicing system
                    in real time. Receive your IRN and QR code instantly — no
                    manual uploads, no compliance gaps.
                  </p>
                  <a
                    href="/fbr-integration/"
                    class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-1"
                  >
                    See how it works
                    <svg
                      class="w-3 h-3 md:w-4 md:h-4"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right - Content -->
          <div class="mt-6 lg:mt-0">
            <h2
              class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 md:mb-6 leading-tight"
            >
              One platform for sales, stock, and FBR compliance
            </h2>
            <p
              class="text-sm md:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed"
            >
              Centralise your contacts, track every deal stage, and get live
              updates — so your team always knows what to do next. Your sales
              data, inventory, and FBR reports all in one place. No spreadsheet
              juggling. No missed deadlines.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/contact/?message=I'd like to learn more about your tools and features."
